    <h2>What's all the TALKing about?</h2>
    <p>Talk is where all the conversations are happening regarding Kiez Burn. It might seem overwhelming at first, but you can navigate to public groups and join conversations in Threads that interest you. We recommend at a minimum you join <a href="https://talk.kiezburn.org/g/JVNW8EpX/kiez-burn-2019-planning">Kiez Burn 2019 Planning</a> Group.</p>

    <p class="more"><a href="https://talk.kiezburn.org/d/4632pc0x/getting-started-with-talk-">Getting Started with Talk</a></p>
